{"title":"搜身——悲殖民地风景","authors":["壶井繁治"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——悲殖民地风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔日本〕壶井繁治"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个出奇的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静悄悄的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京浜重工业区的一角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我独自行走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过无情的水泥马路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到川崎码头去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是三菱石油公司的曲线型仓库"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铝质的油池之群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正月的青钢色的天空里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞绕着在搜索什么呢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的冷峻的眼中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为仇恨之的的飞机？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿，是日本？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是美国呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一步一步，拖着沉重的步子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印出一个个黑色的疑问号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的脚，确是踏在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本的道路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向码头去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日本的晴朗的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却飞着美国的飞机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群群黑色的飞蛾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地在我眼前飞过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过最短的距离，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向朝鲜的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去进行大批的屠杀和破坏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆自行车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲着我过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑着一个穿劳动服的青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手抓着车档，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着一个苹果在咬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了这辆车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没有一个行人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从水泥路上走过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清楚地望见海边的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"P ．D．工厂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拱形的大门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴白钢盔的高个儿兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在搜查"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个油污的日本工人的身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裤子，口袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸进手去搜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也来搜吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜我的身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外口袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里口袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裤子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有我的心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔适夷译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}